These are Puzzles for 5x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-2-1::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, cain, bluemaster, old-henry
City: rome, miami, london, new-york
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, soy-milk, water, fanta
4 different games are played: bridge, monopoly, backgammon, chess
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, october, july, august
 1. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person traveling to miami##1
 2. the person drinking fanta is between the fonseca-smoker and the person who's birthday is in august##2
 3. the person playing bridge is the person who's birthday is in august##1
 4. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in november is between the fonseca-smoker and the person drinking water##2
 6. the person playing chess is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in october is the bluemaster-smoker##1
 8. the old-henry-smoker is on the left of the person traveling to new-york##1
 9. the person traveling to london is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
10. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the fonseca-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |         3          |     4     |
| Cigar           | bluemaster | fonseca   | old-henry | cain |
| City   | rome      | miami | london              | new-york |
| Beverage   | 7up       | soy-milk     | fanta               | water    |
| Game           | monopoly        | backgammon     | chess           | bridge       |
| Birthday     | october | july     | november                | august      |

