 2. the person playing domino is on the right of the person traveling to venice##1
 3. the dutch is between the person traveling to nizza and the siglo-smoker##2
 4. the person playing billiard is the cottage house##1
 5. the alhambra-smoker is the dutch##1
 6. the chinese is on the left of the japanese##1
 7. the pakistani is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
 8. the cape-cod house is on the left of the chinese##1
 9. the colonial house is on the left of the japanese##1
10. the chinese is on the left of the havana-smoker##1
11. the cottage house is the person traveling to nizza##1
12. the person traveling to venice is the chinese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |        1        |     2      |       3        |      4      |
