The people use 4 different means of transport: trike, tram, helicopter, quad-bike
4 different games are played: go, whist, scrabble, billiard
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, dunhill, vegafina, alhambra
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: poppy, orchid, dahlia, rose
 1. the person playing go is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
 2. the baccarat-smoker is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
 3. the baccarat-smoker is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
 4. the baccarat-smoker is the person who growsorchid##1
 5. the dunhill-smoker is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 6. the person drinking sprite is between the person driving the tram and the person who growspoppy##2
 7. the person playing go is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 8. the person drinking mirinda is the person who growsdahlia##1
 9. the person playing go is the alhambra-smoker##1
10. the person playing whist is on the far left##1
11. the person playing whist is the person who growspoppy##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| Beverage          | soy-milk    | sprite  | almond-milk | mirinda |
| Transport   | trike   | helicopter        | tram | quad-bike     |
