 1. the ranch-style house is the person who growsorchid##1
 2. the craftsman house is between the person watching time-travel movies and the person watching superhero movies##2
 3. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person traveling to marseilles##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in july is the person traveling to marseilles##1
 5. the person watching superhero movies is between the person traveling to marseilles and the colonial house##2
 6. the person traveling to new-york is on the far left##1
 7. the person traveling to venice is on the right of the person watching animation movies##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in october is the palace house##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in september is between the craftsman house and the person watching animation movies##2
10. the person who growsiris is on the far left##1
11. the person who growslily is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |      3      |      4       |
| Birthday      | march     | september | july    | october          |
