 2. the person who likes apricot is on the left of the fan gospel##1
 3. the townhouse house is on the right of the ranch-style house##1
 4. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person who likes ebony##1
 5. the person who's sport is climbing is on the far right##1
 6. the fan house is on the right of the townhouse house##1
 7. the person who likes ebony is on the right of the person traveling to prague##1
 8. the ranch-style house is on the right of the person who likes blood-red##1
 9. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person traveling to boston##1
10. the person who's sport is biathlon is between the person who's sport is skateboarding and the person traveling to rome##2
11. the fan classical is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1
12. the tower house is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
