4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, pall-mall, oliveros, siglo
 1. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 2. the person who's hobby is collecting is between the person traveling to hannover and the oliveros-smoker##2
 3. the person traveling to edinburgh is between the person watching adventure movies and the person watching spy movies##2
 4. the bolivar-smoker is the person who's birthday is in february##1
 5. the person who's hobby is board-games is the person who's birthday is in september##1
 6. the person traveling to edinburgh is the person watching documentary movies##1
 7. the siglo-smoker is the person watching adventure movies##1
 8. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the pall-mall-smoker##1
 9. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
10. the person traveling to paris is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
11. the person who's hobby is video-games is between the person who's birthday is in september and the siglo-smoker##2
12. the person who's hobby is collecting is between the bolivar-smoker and the person watching documentary movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |       2        |    3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre      | spy      | documentary         | adventure | thriller      |
| Birthday           | september | may | june | february     |
| City   | paris         | edinburgh          | london  | hannover |
| Hobby         | board-games        | video-games  | collecting | drawing   |
| Cigar     | pall-mall    | oliveros         | siglo     | bolivar     |

