.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-2-18::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: mauve, grey, aquamarine, turquise
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, dannemann, game, bongani
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, cola, sprite, fanta
There are 4 different nationalities: turkish, american, argentine, indian
House: farmhouse, gothic-revival, tower, modern
 1. the person drinking fanta is between the argentine and the gothic-revival house##2
 2. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the bongani-smoker##1
 3. the american is the tower house##1
 4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far right##1
 5. the indian is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
 6. the american is on the right of the person who likes grey##1
 7. the person who likes mauve is the bongani-smoker##1
 8. the dannemann-smoker is on the right of the game-smoker##1
 9. the person who likes turquise is on the left of the game-smoker##1
10. the indian is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
11. the person who likes turquise is between the bongani-smoker and the turkish##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |   4    |
| Color          | mauve  | turquise  | grey  | aquamarine   |
| Cigar   | bongani     | aristoff | game     | dannemann |
| Beverage           | sprite   | fanta     | cola      | hot-chocolate   |
| Nationality         | argentine   | indian    | turkish  | american |
| House     | farmhouse | modern     | gothic-revival | tower |

