.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-2-19::.
There 4 different types of food: tomato, pumpkin, orange, artichoke
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, rugby, climbing, volleyball
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, zinnia, lily, rose
There are 4 different nationalities: spanish, pakistani, mexican, egyptian
4 different games are played: canasta, backgammon, mah-jongg, go
 1. the person who growslily is the person who's sport is rugby##1
 2. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the person who growslily##1
 3. the person eating pumpkin is between the egyptian and the person who growsrose##2
 4. the person who growsrose is the spanish##1
 5. the person eating tomato is between the person eating pumpkin and the person playing go##2
 6. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 7. the mexican is on the far right##1
 8. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is the person playing mah-jongg##1
 9. the person eating pumpkin is on the right of the person who growsamaryllis##1
10. the person eating orange is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |      3       |       4       |
| Food      | artichoke    | pumpkin     | tomato        | orange          |
| Sport         | volleyball | rugby   | ice-hockey        | climbing |
| Flower           | amaryllis   | lily | rose | zinnia      |
| Nationality   | egyptian    | pakistani      | spanish          | mexican        |
| Game     | canasta  | backgammon   | mah-jongg      | go           |

