.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-2-20::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, june, november, march
The people have 4 different jobs:  dressmaker, accountant, entrepreneur, chef
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, blend, siglo, alhambra
City: hannover, colone, miami, boston
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: sunflower, marigold, rose, poppy
 1. the chef is the blend-smoker##1
 2. the person who growspoppy is between the alhambra-smoker and the person traveling to hannover##2
 3. the person who growsmarigold is between the person traveling to colone and the person who growsrose##2
 4. the accountant is on the right of the chef##1
 5. the entrepreneur is on the right of the person traveling to colone##1
 6. the person traveling to colone is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the chef##1
 8. the entrepreneur is the person traveling to miami##1
 9. the person who growsmarigold is on the left of the person who growsrose##1
10. the person who's birthday is in may is the bolivar-smoker##1
11. the bolivar-smoker is the person traveling to boston##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |      3      |      4       |
| Birthday         | november  | june | march | may |
| Job   | chef      | accountant   | entrepreneur      | dressmaker    |
| Cigar   | blend  | siglo | alhambra        | bolivar     |
| City         | hannover  | colone  | miami     | boston      |
| Flower     | sunflower | poppy      | marigold   | rose       |

 